    <item>
      <title>特朗普进军 2024 年大选 哈里斯向华尔街高层示好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/wall-street-brass-courted-by-harris-as-trump-makes-2024-inroads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯正在与美国企业高层培养关系，向那些有迹象表明将在 11 月大选中大力支持共和党人唐纳德·特朗普的团体伸出了橄榄枝。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/wall-street-brass-courted-by-harris-as-trump-makes-2024-inroads</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 17:45:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国相对于德国的风险溢价达到 2012 年以来的最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/france-s-risk-premium-over-germany-closes-at-highest-since-2012</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们越来越担心，争夺法国即将到来的立法选举的政党可能会进一步导致公共财政膨胀，投资者对法国债券的持有要求比对更安全的德国债券更高的溢价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/france-s-risk-premium-over-germany-closes-at-highest-since-2012</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 16:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度教徒因在日内瓦别墅剥削仆人被判有罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/hindujas-found-guilty-of-exploitation-of-servants-at-swiss-villa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁欣杜贾家族的四名成员因在日内瓦别墅中剥削薪水微薄的仆人而被判有罪，这一判决对印度最富有和最有影响力的家族之一的瑞士分支来说是毁灭性的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/hindujas-found-guilty-of-exploitation-of-servants-at-swiss-villa</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 15:38:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党获得的大额捐款比英国保守党多 14 倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/labour-and-reform-lead-uk-conservatives-on-campaign-donations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国大选竞选活动的第二周，英国工党反对派获得的大额捐款至少是首相里希·苏纳克领导的保守党的 14 倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/labour-and-reform-lead-uk-conservatives-on-campaign-donations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱沙尼亚与俄罗斯边境设置界线 暂停通行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/lines-at-border-with-russia-leave-estonia-mulling-halt-to-travel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱沙尼亚表示，将于周末关闭这个波罗的海国家前往俄罗斯的主要航线，称边境长队对健康和公共秩序构成了威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/lines-at-border-with-russia-leave-estonia-mulling-halt-to-travel</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 10:06:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国司法部撤销对 TikTok 误导美国消费者的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/doj-drops-tiktok-claims-raised-by-ftc-over-misleading-consumers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部撤销了针对字节跳动有限公司旗下 TikTok 的两项拟议指控之一，计划在今年晚些时候将消费者保护诉讼的重点放在儿童隐私上，而不是指控该视频共享平台在数据安全方面误导消费者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/doj-drops-tiktok-claims-raised-by-ftc-over-misleading-consumers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 22:06:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国或将效仿苏纳克的庇护计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/germany-weighs-copying-uk-asylum-plan-as-scholz-faces-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国政府承认，邻国大力宣传的移民计划并没有取得很好的效果。但由于这一问题暴露了其关键的政治弱点，德国政府仍准备继续推进，以抵御随时准备发起攻击的右翼势力的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/germany-weighs-copying-uk-asylum-plan-as-scholz-faces-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 22:00:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
